    "details": {
      "biography": "<p>A Jikegida wearing a construction exoskeleton gains 20 hit points, a +2 bonus to hit, and a +2 bonus on all damage rolls or Shock. Many exoskeletons incorporate the natural defenses or abilities of the creatures used in their construction, with poison sprays, tremendous mobility, sonic shrieks, or other offensive or defensive abilities.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #191813;\">Two attacks per round. Shock ignores AC value.</span></p>",
